</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="f2d16bb1-7a89-4891-afab-115124ecae97" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0.0.0" class="r-k4q3oo" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="dfdc8e2f-ea30-4a35-9655-27152bbe73e4" aria-controls="replo-:R2k2u:" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0.0.0.0" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-kklwtl"><div data-rid="52b45a13-2ea8-4bf5-aba7-0adf6a515562" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0.0.0.0.0" class="r-hyu6xj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Is this product clinically tested? </p></span></div><div data-rid="a9446906-886a-4dc6-a9a4-4036840aa22a" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0.0.0.0.0" class="r-wowmy5"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-1xngixw" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R2k2u:" aria-controls="replo-:R2k2u:"><div data-rid="23cba33b-38c2-49cb-b429-ccbd5db07ae7" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0.0.0.0" class="r-11vmrkl"><div data-rid="a89c75c6-8c6b-414c-bf7c-222ab4b11508" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0.0.0.0.0" class="r-1chj5za alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Yes, our Freedom of Expression Line Limiter has been clinically proven to reduce laugh lines, lip lines, forehead creases, and lines around the crow's feet area.</p><br><p><strong>Based on an Instrumental analyses with 28 participants (age 40-64) in a 4 weeks clinical study</strong></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="b2416214-4c60-4a30-a8ff-8ac04416a2fe" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0.0.0" class="r-18nww6f" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="c76cdff8-4fdd-45f1-a654-5d86182328e9" aria-controls="replo-:R3k2u:" data-replo-repeated-index=".0.0.0.0.0" tabindex="0" role="butt